#TwinFlame #Energy #Forecast 15th - 21st May: “Return of the King”🔥The Lion Dominates Collective Soul Development After 17 Years Of Purification.  Can You Live With An Open Heart In A World Of Fear❓There's a lot going on in the cosmic energies right now. For the first time in almost two decades the North Node - representing collective soul development - moves retrograde into Leo. This means there's a lot of old stuff being stirred up. It's the first time the North Node visits Leo since year 1999-2000, meaning there are issues in the collective development that require resolution - something from that time is recurring: themes, tendencies, conflicts…
On a world scale, increasing conflict brewing in the Middle East and resulting fear around the globe is a corresponding theme. Conflict between opposing views and values. With Ego comes conflict, because the ego is based in perceiving the world as “you vs me”. For #TwinFlames this could pose a problem - as discussed before, perceptions of difference and separation are one of the core blocks to Twin pairs coming together.
For you personally Spirit indicates, look back. What were you experiencing in 1999-2000 and how does it relate to your current situation? How can you handle things differently now? How have you grown as a person? A theme for Twin Flames in this period is a shift from the feminine polarity Twin shouldering most of the burden, to the masculine being activated to carry out more work "above ground". With Moon conjunct Pluto retrograde early in the week, old unconscious feelings are stirred up - this is set to be an intense period but try to treat it like you would a detox of the physical body. Know that any latent emotions rising up are being stirred so you can clear them. Then do so. Once you learn metaphysical energy clearing methods you can use them with ease any time, anywhere. #TwinFlameUnion is not just about softening or "upgrading" the Masculine. It’s about clearing the Feminine’s need of others so she can become whole within and attract a relationship that’s truly worthy of her: Safe in the knowing that she doesn’t need her counterpart, she chooses him out of love...
